 548:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** * \brief
 549:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  Gets the specified parameter value from the \ref group_structures.
 550:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *
 551:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** * \details
 552:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  This function gets the value of the specified parameter by the paramId
 553:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  argument. The paramId for each register is available in the
 554:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  CapSense_1 RegisterMap header file as
 555:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  CapSense_1_<ParameterName>_PARAM_ID. The paramId is a special
 556:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  enumerated value generated by the customizer. The format of paramId is as
 557:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  follows:
 558:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *    1. [ byte 3 byte 2 byte 1 byte 0 ]
 559:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *    2. [ TTWFCCCC UIIIIIII MMMMMMMM LLLLLLLL ]
 560:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *    3. T - encodes the parameter type:
 561:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *      - 01b: uint8
