 853:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** * \brief
 854:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  Reports if the specified sensor in the widget detects a touch.
 855:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *
 856:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** * \details
 857:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  This function reports if the specified sensor in the widget has detected a
 858:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  touch or not by extracting information from the wdgtStatus registers
ARM GAS  C:\Users\Bryce\AppData\Local\Temp\ccLuOGF3.s 			page 26


 859:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  (CapSense_1_WDGT_STATUS<X>_VALUE). This function does not process the
