 861:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *
 862:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  For proximity sensors, this function returns the proximity detection status. To
 863:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  get the finger touch status of proximity sensors, use the
 864:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  CapSense_1_IsProximitySensorActive() function.
