 866:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** * \param widgetId
 867:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  Specifies the ID number of the widget.
 868:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  A macro for the widget ID can be found in the CapSense_1 Configuration header
 869:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** *  file defined as CapSense_1_<WidgetName>_WDGT_ID.
 870:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Structure.c **** 
